data.description: Lago Mar Master Planned Community offers limited Contemporary modern style with cool package grays and white netural tones for a unique design. Features 4/3/ flex space with closet (great 5th bedroom). Architectural design modern vibe with  contemporary glass front door in a pop of color adding curb appeal and an option to create your personal touch. Walk in pantry. Builder upgrades Extended foyer,  42" crisp white cabinets with gorgeous backsplash, Larger Family area and Dining, Island seats 4, Tile flooring except bedrooms with upgrade carpet, Extra window with treatments adding more natural light, primary with two linens and a large walk in closet, (1) secondary with a linen area. Extended Covered patio with recessed lighting and plumb for gas, irrigations system. Located in the spacious newer section. Better than new!!
